2851 - Paints, Varnishes, Lacquers, Enamels and Allied Products Summary > RUST-OLEUM AUSTRALIA & NEW ZEALAND PTY LTD is an Australian proprietary company. Its operations cover paints, varnishes, lacquers, enamels and allied products. The company is involved in the import and export of goods. RUST-OLEUM AUSTRALIA & NEW ZEALAND PTY LTD is headquartered in Mount Waverley, Victoria. It is headed by director Nigel David St Clair Meakins. For the 2024 financial year, the company reported revenue of $30.01 million. Its net profit totalled $5.76 million.
